sentences.sentence: OBJECTIVE To observe the spermicidal effect of compound nonoxynol vaginal gel in vitro.
sentences.translation: 目的：观察复方凝胶制剂的体外杀精效果。

sentences.sentence: Objective: To study the effect of tea saponin in ameliorating nonoxynol (N-9) spermicidal action in vitro.
sentences.translation: 目的：观察茶皂素对壬苯醇醚(N 9)的杀精增效作用。

sentences.sentence: While I was digging around the web looking for more information on Monsanto, I stumbled across this page about spermicidal corn and population control. She cites the following two chilling articles ?
